  <entry>
    <title>WSL开启systemd后运行exe文件报错Exec format error的解决办法</title>
    <link href="/2022/11/01/WSL%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFsystemd%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cexe%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99Exec-format-error%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <url>/2022/11/01/WSL%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFsystemd%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cexe%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99Exec-format-error%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>报错如图所示</p><img src="/2022/11/01/WSL%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFsystemd%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8Cexe%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99Exec-format-error%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/image-20221127121014384.png" class="" title="image-20221127121014384"><p>解决办法：</p><ol><li><p>创建一个名为<code>WSLInterop.conf</code>的文件，内容为</p><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ruby"><span class="hljs-symbol">:WSLInterop</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:M</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:MZ</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:/init</span><span class="hljs-symbol">:PF</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>保存后放在<code>/usr/lib/binfmt.d</code>目录下</p></li><li><p>使用<code>PowerShell</code>输入<code>wsl --shutdown</code>重启<code>WSL</code>即可</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>使用Hexo搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2022/10/09/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2022/10/09/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>安装Node.js和Git并安装</p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/">Download | Node.js (nodejs.org)</a></p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/">Git (git-scm.com)</a></p></li><li><p>使用npm -v检查安装情况</p></li><li><p>安装hexo</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>创建用于存放博客文件的文件夹并初始化</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs powershell">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;<br>npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置config</p></li><li><p>基础命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean//清除缓存文件和已生成的静态文件<br>hexo g//生成静态文件<br>hexo s//启动本地服务<br>hexo d//push到github<br>hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;title&quot;</span>//新建一个名为title的博文<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  
